{"tid":635262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"謝偉俊倡郵輪碼頭「活化」做龕場","createTime":"2018-04-20T03:54:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-20T12:38:05.000Z","uid":2810,"like":147,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"f70260bdef7740c42c1ff8afe468126a04c59b12","tid":635262,"uid":2810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T03:54:44.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】本港土地問題嚴峻，連先人都受波及。據食環署就財政預算案開支答覆，本港上年骨灰龕位累計輪候申請總數已逾2.9萬宗，平均輪候46個月。<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">立法會議員謝偉俊就話，郵輪碼頭大樓長年冷清，猶如「東九停屍間」，倒不如將大樓「活化」，改建做大型骨灰龕場。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n謝偉俊話，郵輪碼頭大樓商舖十室九空，質疑政府耗資82億公帑投資，都無經濟效益，提議商經局不如將碼頭大樓改建做大型龕場，「活化」碼頭。佢問局方「會否死馬當活馬醫」，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">出售龕位，按月收管理費，喺春秋二祭同藉「解穢酒」帶旺人流；仲提議邀請設計法國羅浮宮嘅建築師貝聿銘，喺碼頭末端起新饒宗頤紀念館，將碼頭活化做「慎終追遠」同「弘揚國學旅遊新景點」。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n商經局常任秘書長（工商及旅遊）容偉雄答覆話，碼頭主要目的係畀郵輪停泊，無空間改建做骨灰龕；話建議無助增加人流同增添活力，而碼頭末端亦無空間設新景點。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180420/s00002/1524160102661?web_push=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180420%2Fs00002%2F1524160102661%3Fweb_push%3D1&d=jxAsTADpIS2eYGc%2BVBnRADA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=f2b69c3b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180420%2Fs00002%2F1524160102661%3Fweb_push%3D1&h=b1e34431\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180420/s00002/1524160102661?web_push=1</a>"},{"pid":"c7cb168f5d0d1dca1da087bb1c6afaf30ba4a3c1","tid":635262,"uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:00:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f92ae06d1e0c6b24879ca2555f8396ad09061588","tid":635262,"uid":37757,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:01:20.000Z","msg":"大澳比生人, 維港比